<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wèi bù xiǔ zhī guó 迦南1166</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wèi bù xiǔ zhī guó bēn pǎo de rén, shén bì gěi nǐ lì liàng.
 wèi fú yīn tà shàng yì xiāng de rén, shén bì gěi nǐ fāng xiàng.
 bǎ cái bǎo zǎn jī zài tiān shàng de rén, shén bì zuò nǐ bǎo zhàng.
 wèi shén jiā rì yè jǐng xǐng de rén, shén shì nǐ de liàng guāng.
 zài fú shì zhǔ de rén hǎi zhōng, nǐ shì nǎ yī gè?
 yǒu rén chí shǒu yǒu rén mí lù, yǒu rén yǐ duò luò.
 rì guāng zhī xià jǐn dōu xū kōng, yǒng cún de shì shén de guó.
 wèi bù xiǔ zhī guó qù bēn pǎo, shí jī mò cuò guò.
 zài fú shì zhǔ de rén hǎi zhōng, nǐ shì nǎ yī gè?
 wèi bù xiǔ zhī guó qù bēn pǎo, shí jī mò cuò guò.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
